data.description:
The Reserve at Sugartree on the Brazos!! Brock ISD. This stunning well maintained home is situated on 3 beautiful acres with lots of mature trees.
Uniquely styled with upgrades from floor to ceiling. Open concept kitchen with 2 enormous islands and oversized dining room perfect for holiday gatherings. Massive windows provide lots of natural light with amazing views of the backyard and wildlife. Enjoy peaceful evenings on the back porch in front of the wood burning fireplace. Also pre wired for TV. Ample room for barn, shop and swimming pool for the hot Texas summer days. This home is a entertainers dream!!  Upstairs bathroom laundry have been recently added.
